comment:
Ori and the Will of the Wisps Walkthrough Gameplay Part 1 includes a Review, Prologue, Reaction, Act 1 and Campaign Mission 1 of the Ori and the Will of the Wisps Single Player Story Campaign for Xbox One X and PC. This Ori and the Will of the Wisps (the sequel to Ori and the Blind Forest) Story Campaign Walkthrough will include the Full Game. Ori and the Will of the Wisps Walkthrough Part 1 will include a Review, Ori, Ku, Naru, Gumo, All Bosses, Cinematics, Cut Scenes, OST, Soundtrack, Story Missions, Main Missions, New Gameplay, DLC, all Single Player Campaign Missions and the Ending. Thanks Microsoft for giving me Ori and the Will of the Wisps!
